1. *Koraka* mi je ostalo još samo nekoliko do cilja. (I have only a few *steps* left to reach the finish line.)
2. *Korakom* po korak, uspeo sam da pređem preko reke. (I managed to cross the river *step by step*.)
3. Udaljenost između dve tačke se meri u *koracima*. (The distance between two points is measured in *steps*.)
4. Želim da napravim *korak* napred u svojoj karijeri. (I want to take a *step* forward in my career.)
5. Snažan *korak* u pravom smeru je ključ ka uspehu. (A strong *step* in the right direction is the key to success.)
6. Bilo je čudno čuti *korake* u praznom hodniku. (It was strange to hear *footsteps* in an empty hallway.)
7. Šta ćeš uraditi ako ti neko stane na *korak*? (What will you do if someone stops you in your *tracks*?)
8. Moramo pratiti svaki *korak* protivnika. (We have to follow every *move* of our opponent.)